@startuml PY-013-erd
title PY-013 · Learner Profile + Progress — ERD

skinparam backgroundColor #1e1e2e
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #2a2a3d
  BorderColor #555577
  FontColor #cdd6f4
  HeaderBackgroundColor #313244
}
skinparam ArrowColor #89b4fa
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #313244
skinparam NoteBorderColor #555577
skinparam NoteFontColor #cdd6f4

entity "profiles" as Profile {
  * id         : uuid  <<PK, default gen_random_uuid()>>
  --
  * username   : text  <<unique, not null>>
  * created_at : timestamptz <<default now()>>
}

note right of Profile
  Created on first visit when
  learner enters their username.
  No password — username is the
  only identifier at MVP.
  profile_id stored in localStorage
  to re-identify the learner on
  subsequent visits.
end note

entity "path_completions" as Completion {
  * id          : uuid  <<PK, default gen_random_uuid()>>
  --
  * profile_id  : uuid  <<FK → profiles.id>>
  * skill_id    : text  <<e.g. "variables">>
  * level       : text  <<"easy" | "mid" | "hard">>
  * xp_awarded  : int
  * completed_at: timestamptz <<default now()>>
  --
  unique(profile_id, skill_id, level)
}

note right of Completion
  One row per completed path.
  The unique constraint prevents
  duplicate XP awards.
  XP total = SUM(xp_awarded)
  for a given profile_id.
end note

Profile "1" --o{ "0..*" Completion : has

note bottom of Profile
  Derived fields (computed at query time,
  never stored):
    total_xp      = SUM(xp_awarded)
    skills_complete = COUNT of skill_ids
                      where all 3 levels present
    projects_complete = 0 until PY-007+
end note

@enduml
